parameters:
VIP Customer: "What are you saying, Juri-chan. You can earn several
times more by appearing in AV than your current job."
VIP Customer: "Though, you won't be getting any appearance fee, haha!"

Manager: "Screaming is useless, the soundproofing in this room is
perfect. No one will come to help."
Juri: "That voice, Manager!? Why are you doing this..."

Manager: "You were our top earner, but this business makes several
times more. Just give up quietly."

VIP Customer: "This is a business that the manager and I started
together."
VIP Customer: "Forced AV appearances without acting..."

VIP Customer: "Illegal AV like this sells for a high price in the
underworld."
Juri: "I don't want this! Somebody! Somebody help me--!!"

VIP Customer: "I've been telling you. It's no use calling for help.
This is a soundproofed sealed room, you'll work here until you die, so
be prepared."

parameters.name: ポニーセレスのテーマ

parameters:
Yui: "I've heard your conversation. Are you prepared for what's
coming, making girls go through such horrible things?"
VIP Customer: "Manager, what's the meaning of this?"

Yui: "Just a frail bunny who stumbled into this scary room by bad
luck."
Manager: "Somebody! Come here! An intruder has broken in!!"

Yui: "Oh? But I thought the soundproofing was perfect. No one should
hear the voices from this room outside."

Manager: "Between this and the Mamiko incident, it's just one disaster
after another!"

Yui: "Just release the girls quietly and turn yourself in to the
police. If you do, you won't end up like your friend over there."

Manager: "Don't order me around! Acting all high and mighty just
because you're a woman!"

Yui: "Juri-san, I've come to save you. Don't worry, everything is
going to be okay now."

And so, Yui rescued the girls who had been confined and handed over
the manager and VIP customer to the police.

Afterward, a police investigation was conducted on the Bunny-Girl
Cabaret Club Agas, revealing all its misdeeds, leading to its closure.
